# Web3 Platform Landing Page — Environment Variables
#
# Copy this file to `.env` (gitignored) and fill in the values for local
# development. Variables prefixed with `VITE_` are exposed to client-side
# code by Vite at build time.

# WalletConnect Cloud project identifier.
# Required by RainbowKit / wagmi to enable WalletConnect-based wallet
# connections (mobile wallets via QR code, etc.).
#
# How to obtain:
#   1. Sign up / log in at https://cloud.walletconnect.com
#   2. Create a new project (any name).
#   3. Copy the generated "Project ID" and paste it below.
VITE_WALLETCONNECT_PROJECT_ID=your_walletconnect_project_id_here
